r\"><div class=\"botslice_quote\"></div></div><br />&nbsp;Amen, brother----- If I had a son, (and I do) I would tell him not to get anywhere near this field, unless you are completely desperate. Unfortunately, in this &quot;booming&quot; job market many people are, and that's why this job and most others have declined. It may get better but not in my lifetime. My advice---&quot;don't!&quot;",
